Sherlock Mysteries is mystery investigation game where you are part of a group, lead by Mr Wiggins,  helping Sherlock Holmes to solve crimes on the streets of Victorian London. You start with case introduction by Mr Holmes and then can go and investigate any number of London people or locations. Visiting each relevant location will unravel peace of story, that can give you new clues or hint other locations you can visit.

Remember, you can finish case and listen to the final solution at any moment of the game, but your knowledge of what happened will be tested by a series of questions.

Say "start the case" to start investigation and good luck!